ETHERNET-PORT-HISTORIES - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-pmengine-oper:performance-management-history/global/periodic/ethernet-history/ethernet-port-histories/

Retrieve operation of resource: ethernet-port-histories

200 OK
ethernet-port-histories_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error
